@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="legal-page">
    <div class="legal-card">
        <div class="legal-header">
            <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
            <p class="legal-subtitle">
                Strangly respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal data.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-body">
            <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Technical Data:</strong> We automatically collect your IP address, device type, browser type, operating system, and access timestamps.</li>
                <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Interaction logs, session length, and behavior patterns on our platform.</li>
                <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> We use cookies to enhance site functionality and personalize your experience. You may control cookies through your browser settings.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>2. Conversations & Recordings</h2>
            <p>We do <strong>not</strong> record or store any audio or video chats unless explicitly stated in a specific feature or unless required by law. Users are strictly prohibited from recording or capturing others without consent.</p>

            <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>To improve website performance and user experience.</li>
                <li>To monitor and enforce our Rules of Use and protect users from abuse.</li>
                <li>To conduct internal analytics and enhance platform stability and safety.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>4. Data Sharing</h2>
            <p>We do not sell or rent your personal information. We may share anonymized or aggregated data with trusted third-party services (e.g., analytics providers) to improve our services. We may disclose information if required by law or to protect users and the platform.</p>

            <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
            <p>You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal data in accordance with applicable data protection laws (such as GDPR or CCPA). Contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@strangly.com">privacy@strangly.com</a> for any privacy-related requests.</p>

            <h2>6. Security</h2>
            <p>We take reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect your data. However, no system is completely secure. We advise you to avoid sharing sensitive personal information while using the platform.</p>

            <h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Updates will be posted on this page with a revised “Last Updated” date.</p>

            <div class="legal-footer">
                <span><strong>Last Updated:</strong> January 15, 2026</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
